_sText:
This is the first, but also the final public release of the co-operative map coop_vAffel.
I've been working on this map for over 4 months.

Features additional custom textures, one easteregg (which will be found in a green hidden room), and a MASTER OF PUPPETS - button!

In order to complete the map, 4 or more players will have to work together, look up the secret triggers and rooms.
Coop_vAffel is my gift to -[CD]-vAffel's birthday -3th february.

I'll be very glad for feedback! =)

Skybox by G-Flow
